import { Groups } from "@mui/icons-material";
import { Avatar, Box, Card, CardContent, Container, Grid, TextField } from "@mui/material";
import { green } from "@mui/material/colors";

export default function CreateTeamPost() {
    return (
        <main>
            <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', pt: 8, pb: 6, }}>
                <Container maxWidth="xs">
                    <Card>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: green[400] }}>
                                <Groups />
                            </Avatar>
                        </CardContent>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Grid container spacing={2}>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                                    <TextField
                                        autoComplete="given-name"
                                        name="teamName"
                                        required
                                        fullWidth
                                        id="teamName"
                                        label="Team Name"
                                        autoFocus
                                    />
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                                    <TextField

                                    />
                                </Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={12}>
                                    <TextField
                                        margin="normal"
                                        id="outlined-multiline-static"
                                        label="Description"
                                        multiline
                                        rows={4}
                                        fullWidth 
                                    />
                                </Grid>
                            </Grid>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Container>
            </Box>
        </main> 
    )
};
